Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查明固有频率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔  我要就这样冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥  你在说什…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个的控制就还给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等下  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会操控…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪儿跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩德罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是佩德罗他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来联手报仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么高木也在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟昭弘哥一起来站哨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘和高木先回一趟渔火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救  救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正离敌人也挺远的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再来回收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绝啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月哥  那边又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  看来你的心情也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背后全是空隙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说这家伙也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙居然在这个距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙跟我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是阿赖耶识使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有结束喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  新敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要抓稳了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  你就保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  刚才那人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是硬得过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你对昭弘他们动手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那边的小鬼们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我好好干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的就由我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个距离也？那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度竟然这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别小瞧我库达尔·卡德尔大人  以及这台「古辛」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘哥  别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  高木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昌弘快带着人质退下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘哥…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  他过去了  昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那家伙还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂你这混蛋  听得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘…大哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥？  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我…离开昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚吉小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先等一下  还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个放下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啧  真难用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁  塔宾斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这燃料撑不住跟他们打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退信号？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了  拉芙塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我冲得太猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推进剂已经耗得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  昭弘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到渔火了  高木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  高木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舱口还没打开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金属切刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把起重器拿过来  起重器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高…高木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把他放下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  高木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱德  你别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木  高木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先把拉链拉上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航服把血止住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正有医生从大哥的船上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前帮他撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你说帮他撑住…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那  那个  我把需要的东西拿来…            - 喂  谁快拿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出血这么厉害的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 给我                   - 他连内脏都受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备输血袋和消毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有医疗纳米机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见没  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输血袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把医务室的电源接上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没什么大碍了  团长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  今天多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没配备船医  就在行星之间飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出这种判断  可是团长失职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  高木怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽比特小姐说已经没大碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果那群家伙到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  亚吉  看出什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚哈反应炉的固有频率是罗迪架构
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是那么圆滚滚的可爱机动战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个大了一圈的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为样本比较少  没有匹配的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要列出固有频率相似的机体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴巴托斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  完全不相似好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兴趣的话  自己调查去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的问题是  有人在挑衅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  现在你们是存心找我们碴对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  布鲁克·卡巴扬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有提沃兹当靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要摆这么大的谱儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强大的并不是只有提沃兹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔宾斯的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来可别摆出一副哭丧脸喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真有血气方刚的笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  高木怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经稳定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了史提普顿小姐  真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说她是个靠谱的女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  她说你什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说不配备船医就在行星之间航行  是团长的失职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说的没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  关于那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是「布鲁沃兹」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是主要活跃在火星和地球间航路上的海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海贼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  他们盯上了船的货物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是克迪莉娅·蓝那·博斯坦汀这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是如果老实交人  就不会有性命之忧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们上头的人口气不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁沃兹这群海贼  有这么大本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在武斗派里确实是个很出名的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  并不能和提沃兹相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我很在意  他们这次竟然这么强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定背后有个不得了的靠山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很在意  他们怎么知道克迪莉娅小姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有个相当棘手的幕后主使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是  地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  新来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有得到降落到地球的许可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有出身火星的脏猴子在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球就要变臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还是别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙可是来自法立德特务三佐的船上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法立德家可是统领加拉尔号角的「七星」家族之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才更需要教育吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你这种家伙在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是会坏了法立德特务三佐的名声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我的上司是盖里奥·柏德文特务三佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点  您无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏德文家不也是七星家族之一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您肯指点我这样的乡下人  在下十分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能讨伐那些少年就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能给我这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁  我都会追随他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次前往火星的远征  辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这次的工作不负法立德家之名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监察局局长以及统制幕僚长  都有向我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖里奥也是  护卫犬子的任务真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的话  伊兹纳里奥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身为护卫  却受到了帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魅力  就在于你的诚实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我向柏德文卿表达感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惭愧  伊兹纳里奥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  麦克吉利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来能暂时回家放松一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回乡的同时  也有新的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不用回趟家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经见过义父了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想见他那么多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能不见面  还是不见为好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  盖里奥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经三个月没有回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然火星还是太远了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是有出去一趟的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你来  马奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔米莉亚  大家都在看着喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个月没见  你还是个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经是个出色的淑女了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也学会沏红茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿也给马奇沏杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我只是想试试温度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  那个小胡子有什么消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没想到是个有用的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经找到克迪莉娅·蓝那·博斯坦汀的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要报之前的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在出船也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在行动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要雇佣某处的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来跟我伸手要钱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  捕捉铁华团的船的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是远离阿里阿德涅正规路线的昏暗航线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是角笛音都无法到达的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要清理水沟  就交给水老鼠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须更顾全大局才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的火星远征  不就弄清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加拉尔号角的监视耳目  无法到达边境的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  内部还滋生了像科拉尔那样的腐败萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,培育他的  不正是加拉尔号角的现有体制吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这一现有体制的支配力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是加拉尔号角本身  这也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没打算去改变内部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此  才会有棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以动摇现有体制的强力棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说克迪莉娅·蓝那·博斯坦汀能成为那个棋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能那样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了  麦奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  艾尔米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人说不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好好喝啊  艾尔米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚之后  我每天都沏茶给你喝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想重新考虑的话就趁现在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订婚宴之后就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次有人说媒  就借口有任务溜之大吉的任性兄长请不要插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人也很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任务是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又什么都没做成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  克迪莉娅老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  啊  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家想送东西给高木  就收集了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师有什么想送的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  老师在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有能做的事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是探病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易抓到的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然给放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且竟然让曼·罗迪受到这么大的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士比你们有价值多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  好歹找几句借口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥  我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库达尔  开作战会议了  到舰桥来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  你这宇宙老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好反省
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗  昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  我们帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放跑人质的是我  我被打也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你那时  跟对方的驾驶员有在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  全都是那家伙的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们  佩德罗他…佩德罗他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是遭报应了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么报应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是认为高木的事情是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我给出指示的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉不太像你呢  昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像人类之屑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做昌弘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为人类之屑  和我被分开卖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明说了要去接他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不知何时开始  擅自认为他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐在袭击高木的机动战士上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们一起成立铁华团  并肩战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心说是为了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被大姐她们训练也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很开心  所以忘记了自己是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类之屑是不能说开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我遭报应了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们的错  才让昭弘遭报应了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这是因为在铁华团很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以身为团长的我也有责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的  我想说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会承担起全部责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同那叫昌弘的弟弟一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的弟弟  并不是有意与我们为敌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  是你的兄弟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是我们铁华团的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  是这样的吧  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还说你在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太见外了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  大家一起来想负责任的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  还以为在说什么乱七八糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉好吵啊  我都没法睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔  你醒来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都好担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  这好歹是医务室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓死我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒来得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  我们都带点心来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说得那么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果被海盗什么的缠上  搞成这幅样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不明事理的流氓的无聊挑衅罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你想怎么做啊兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是无聊挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一味小瞧也很没意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就教教对方  我们的道理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  沸腾了  沸腾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点把那个白色机动战士搞得一塌糊涂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  垃圾们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在看什么啊  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解闷  要不先从你们开刀好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  机动战士高达  铁血的孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第12话  暗礁
